values:
I would like to dedicate this Christmas song to all of my dearest friends (Henny (your my friend also dammit), Deni, Nilly, Lindsay) but this especially goes out to Deni, who has continued to stand behind me and be my support as well as inspiration for my annual christmas parody that you sick bastards know and love.  The previous one was a quick attempt to tide Deni over, but the following song, is the real deal, I put time and effort into this for you guys.  I love you guys, merry christmas hehe :)

Jolly old Saint Nicholas, 
Lean your ear this way! 
Don't you tell a single soul 
That some of our friends are gay; 
Christmas will be coming soon; 
Now, you fat old fuck
Please procure an abacus 
Just for Linds the Duck


When the clock is striking eight, 
When Henny's fast asleep, 
Down the chimney broad and black, 
With our shit you'll creep; 
Please be sure to wipe you face
Make it white again
Or you'll excite dear Nillifer
With your charcoal skin


Deni wants some whips and chains; 
Nilly wants a sex doll; 
Henny wants a dirty book; 
With pics by Andy Warhol; 
As for me, my superbrain 
Helps me deck the halls; 
If one thing's missing from my list, 
I'm cutting off your balls.
